title: BPRD Series up to 2012
description:
Hi All,

 I saw this is not being seeded and had a number of folks looking for it. This is as complete as I can get, I think all of them up to Pickens County, and #1 of Devils Engine.

 Some of the later ones are on TPB, so you should be able to get them. These are not numbered in order, rather by chapters, which was how I found them organized after doing a little research.

 Hope you like it!
